::: {.cell-output-display}
![Measured K/C signal for the oak reference wood core over the 12 sample series](1_LA-ICPMS_variability_files/figure-html/fig-inter-series-variations-oak-ref-1.png){#fig-inter-series-variations-oak-ref fig-align='center' width=2400}
:::
